  Configure ZAP
  Enabled: yes  Base URL: http://127.0.0.1:8080
  Use /zap status, /zap url <http://host:port>, /zap key <value>, or /zap clear-key.

› 1. Show ZAP status        Check whether the configured ZAP API is reachable right now.
  2. Use localhost default  Save the default ZAP API URL for most machines:
                            http://127.0.0.1:8080.
  3. Disable ZAP            Turn off ZAP-backed tools for future sessions.
  4. Clear API key          Remove the saved ZAP API key from config.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
